Date: Fri, 20 Jun 2025 16:53:56 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 101/111] defconfig: Enable watchdog sysfs for testing
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

This exposes the watchdog timeout in sysfs which allows testing the
watchdog without hardcoding a timeout. Enable it.

Signed-off-by: Nícolas F. R. A. Prado <nfraprado@collabora.com>
---
 arch/arm64/configs/defconfig | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig b/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig
index a0d03894d4fda..b7ade3b9c1d72 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig
+++ b/arch/arm64/configs/defconfig
@@ -741,6 +741,7 @@ CONFIG_SL28CPLD_WATCHDOG=m
 CONFIG_ARM_SP805_WATCHDOG=y
 CONFIG_ARM_SBSA_WATCHDOG=y
 CONFIG_S3C2410_WATCHDOG=y
+CONFIG_WATCHDOG_SYSFS=y
 CONFIG_DW_WATCHDOG=y
 CONFIG_K3_RTI_WATCHDOG=m
 CONFIG_SUNXI_WATCHDOG=m
-- 
2.39.5

